{
  "stem": "15962.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was the street, as I said, in the middle of a row of barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were 30 barracks, roughly, to each camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The front of the camp had a small house which housed the German guards, and had a gate from which people came in and out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was only one gate to each camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then the kitchen and the storage rooms was the next barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at the opposite end was a latrine that consisted of a-- of a concrete block with a bunch of holes in it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And people were led-- each barrack was led to this latrine at specific hours [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to relieve themselves, and-- and similar barrack had just a long pipe with holes in it where people could wash occasionally.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Of course, it was all cold water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this camp-- this particular camp, or segment of Birkenau, was purely devoted to the families from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were-- with the arrival of our transport, there were 10,000 inmates minus all the people who died in the mean-- in the three months since we arrived.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people died daily.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a very heroic Zionist called Fredy Hirsch who was devoted to caring for children, and gave his life to that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he persuaded the SS to set aside one barrack which would serve as a place for children who could not work, could gather during the day, and somehow by-- through the help and instructions of a few chosen educators, could [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] forget a little bit where they-- where we were.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In-- real teaching was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were taught songs and games, and a little bit of here and there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Several hundred.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
